  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After Dark is an RPG Maker horror, adventure, and puzzle game. Play as a teenage girl named Riley who is on the search for her sister after she goes missing in the woods. It's up to you to discover what the forest has in store and the sinister forces at play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be stealthy and stay out of sight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras/261337df7f1e3b719d6472cbc4dacaea.avif?t=1735929352\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras_big/261337df7f1e3b719d6472cbc4dacaea.avif?t=1735929352 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay on your toes and survive monster attacks in quick time events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras/523405dbac03e5326e9a8dc941f68540.avif?t=1735929352\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras_big/523405dbac03e5326e9a8dc941f68540.avif?t=1735929352 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden areas and secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras/259bf95340ab99da7c14cc34b82a5d47.avif?t=1735929352\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras_big/259bf95340ab99da7c14cc34b82a5d47.avif?t=1735929352 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the tools you find on your journey to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras/648c0f3f75aa3a0744a9f7dc3aceae22.avif?t=1735929352\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras_big/648c0f3f75aa3a0744a9f7dc3aceae22.avif?t=1735929352 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CONTROLS: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD / Arrow Keys to move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESC to open the main menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ENTER to interact with objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game trailer by hollowpoint.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After Dark is an RPG Maker horror, adventure, and puzzle game. Play as a teenage girl named Riley who is on the search for her sister after she goes missing in the woods. It's up to you to discover what the forest has in store and the sinister forces at play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be stealthy and stay out of sight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras/261337df7f1e3b719d6472cbc4dacaea.avif?t=1735929352\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras_big/261337df7f1e3b719d6472cbc4dacaea.avif?t=1735929352 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay on your toes and survive monster attacks in quick time events.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras/523405dbac03e5326e9a8dc941f68540.avif?t=1735929352\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras_big/523405dbac03e5326e9a8dc941f68540.avif?t=1735929352 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover hidden areas and secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras/259bf95340ab99da7c14cc34b82a5d47.avif?t=1735929352\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras_big/259bf95340ab99da7c14cc34b82a5d47.avif?t=1735929352 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the tools you find on your journey to progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras/648c0f3f75aa3a0744a9f7dc3aceae22.avif?t=1735929352\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3377510/extras_big/648c0f3f75aa3a0744a9f7dc3aceae22.avif?t=1735929352 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CONTROLS: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WASD / Arrow Keys to move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ESC to open the main menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ENTER to interact with objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game trailer by hollowpoint.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                     </p>",
